Cyclic voltammetry (CV) was carried out for the electrodeposition of GQDs on PARG modified GCE from GQDs aqueous solution (0.002g/mL) in the potential range from 0 to 1.0V at a scan rate of 100mV/s (Fig. 3
                        ). Finally, thin film of PARG-GQDs was obtained at the surface of GCE (See Scheme 2
                        ).
